= Configuration =
For the moment you may wish to adapt https://github.com/mapbox/open-streets-style/blob/45e336e82fe804ab30c8d6d5efa96952580b7018/configure.py
to configure your PostgreSQL paramaters in the .mml file.

= Symbols =
The contents of the symbols directory are referenced as /usr/share/icons/osmt/
in the stylesheet.
